descriptionHtml:
Followin aggregates global blockchain news, integrated with automatic translation and algorithm which provides personal feeds based on your interest.

Here's what value Followin App can bring to you:

👾 PERSONALIZED FEED
Personalized blockchain news will be delivered based on your interest and preference; with automatic translation features, you won't miss any hot news all over the world.

📰 24/7 CRYPTO TRENDING NEWS
24/7 online. Get instant updates and stay informed of the latest trending news in the market.

🔥 TOP DAILY NEWS
AI-picked trending news list helps you get a quick understanding of the day and never miss any important news.

🔍 DISCOVER
Followin will recommend you trending KOLs and hot projects and help you find potential investment opportunities.

📚 IN-DEPTH ANALYSIS
Market insights and in-depth analysis inspire all kinds of users.

There are a few major updates coming with new features:
- Community 🦄
- Aggregate AMA events 🎤

Download Followin App. Staying up to date with all the latest crypto news.

CONTACT US:
Official Website: https://followin.io/
Contact us: support@followin.io
